01:59:05.263 --> 01:59:08.306
♪ Come on, now ♪

01:59:08.391 --> 01:59:11.518
♪ Come on, kid ♪

01:59:11.602 --> 01:59:14.896
♪ Let's hear it ♪

01:59:17.400 --> 01:59:20.694
♪ Let's hear it for me ♪♪

